---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description = 'How Deck Masters collects, uses, and protects your information.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-surface">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 tracking-tight uppercase">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-neutral-500">Last updated: March 9, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-neutral-700">
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy explains how Deck Masters (&quot;we,&quot; &quot;us,&quot; or &quot;our&quot;) collects,
          uses, and protects your information when you visit our website, request an estimate, or otherwise interact
          with us.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>We may collect the following types of information when you interact with us:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Contact details such as your name, phone number, email address, and property address</li>
          <li>Project details you share in forms, calls, or messages</li>
          <li>Communications you send to us (emails, texts, call notes)</li>
          <li>
            Basic technical information about how you use our website (such as IP address, device type, and pages
            visited), often collected through cookies or similar technologies
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Provide estimates and respond to your inquiries</li>
          <li>Schedule visits, manage projects, and communicate about your job</li>
          <li>Send service-related updates, reminders, and support messages</li>
          <li>Improve our services, website, and customer experience</li>
          <li>
            Send marketing or promotional communications if you have opted in (you can opt out at any time)
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">3. Text Messaging and Phone Communications</h2>
        <p>
          If you provide your phone number, we may contact you via phone call or SMS for appointment reminders, project
          updates, and other service-related messages. Message and data rates may apply. You can opt out of SMS at any
          time by replying STOP to a message.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          If you opt in to marketing messages, we may send occasional promotional texts or offers. Consent to receive
          marketing messages is not required to obtain a quote or complete a purchase.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
        <p>
          We do not sell your personal information. We may share limited information with trusted third-party service
          providers who help us operate our business (for example, scheduling, CRM, or messaging platforms). These
          providers are only permitted to use your information to perform services on our behalf.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or
          destruction. However, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure, and we cannot guarantee
          absolute security.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">6. Your Choices</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Opt out of marketing emails or texts by using the unsubscribe or STOP instructions in the message</li>
          <li>Update or correct your contact details by reaching out to us</li>
          <li>Disable cookies in your browser settings, which may affect how the site functions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">7. Children&apos;s Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Our services are intended for adults and homeowners. We do not knowingly collect personal information from
          children under 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so we
          can remove it.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we do, we will update the &quot;Last updated&quot;
          date above. Continued use of our website or services after changes become effective constitutes your
          acceptance of the updated Policy.
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-6 font-semibold text-neutral-900 text-base">9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or how we handle your information, please contact us using the
          information on our Contact page.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-neutral-500">
          This Privacy Policy is intended to provide a clear, general overview of how we handle your information. Your
          specific project or agreement may include additional terms that supplement this Policy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

